{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-archived-blog-template-js","path":"/2015/05/51-travel-in-yichang/","result":{"data":{"archivedBlogPostJson":{"categories":[{"path":"/category/entertainment/","name":"生活娱乐活动"}],"tags":[{"name":"三峡","path":"/tag/three-gorges/"},{"name":"宜昌","path":"/tag/yichang/"},{"name":"旅游","path":"/tag/travel/"},{"name":"清江画廊","path":"/tag/qingjianghualang/"},{"name":"潜江","path":"/tag/qianjiang/"},{"name":"美食","path":"/tag/food/"},{"name":"自驾","path":"/tag/self-driving/"},{"name":"长阳","path":"/tag/changyang/"}],"featured_media":{"source_url":"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/未标题-1.jpg"},"path":"/2015/05/51-travel-in-yichang/","date":"2015-05-05T05:01:50.000Z","excerpt":"好难得的一次家庭出游，提前一个月计划好，叫上二姨、小姨、姨爹一同到宜昌去，游长阳、三峡，到潜江吃虾子，饱口福、 … ","title":"五一游宜昌三峡长阳潜江","content":"<p>好难得的一次家庭出游，提前一个月计划好，叫上二姨、小姨、姨爹一同到宜昌去，游长阳、三峡，到潜江吃虾子，饱口福、饱眼福，还参观妈妈曾经工作过的“长阳二工区”。</p>\n<p><embed width=\"480\" height=\"400\" align=\"middle\" src=\"//player.youku.com/player.php/sid/XOTQ4NDg2Mzg4/v.swf\" type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\"/></p>\n<p>在家又把家里老照片翻出来看，我帅气的爸爸和清纯的妈妈，来张妈妈的照片。</p>\n<p><figure id=\"attachment_1753\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1753\" style=\"width: 514px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/DSC_0196_1985mother.jpg\"><img width=\"514\" height=\"800\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1753\" alt=\"妈妈1985年游乐山大佛\" src=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/DSC_0196_1985mother.jpg\" srcset=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/DSC_0196_1985mother.jpg 514w, https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/DSC_0196_1985mother-193x300.jpg 193w, https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/DSC_0196_1985mother-370x576.jpg 370w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 514px) 100vw, 514px\" /></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1753\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">妈妈1985年游乐山大佛</figcaption></figure></p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2015/05/51-travel-in-yichang/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["251939775","3675143411","4019104361"]}